Titolo: Game & Watch Gallery

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Game & Watch Gallery is a game developed by Nintendo and released in 1997 for the Game Boy. It is the second game in the Game & Watch Gallery series, after Game Boy Gallery. It is known as Game Boy Gallery (ゲームボーイギャラリー, Gēmu Bōi Gyararii) in Japan, and as Game Boy Gallery 2 in Australia. This game is the only game in the Game & Watch Gallery series to have its own soundtrack. The soundtrack also included updated versions of the music featured in the game.
A sequel, called Game & Watch Gallery 2, was released for the Game Boy in 1997 and for the Game Boy Color in 1998.